  <summary date="2019-02-07T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Providing Accountability Through Transparency Act of 2019

This bill requires the notice of a proposed rule by a federal agency to include the Internet address of a summary of the rule. The summary must be 100 words or fewer, written in plain language, and posted on regulations.gov.</summary>
